                                                                                                                    QUERY PLAN                                                                                                                    
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Sort
   Sort Key: (bson_orderby(bson_dollar_project(agg_stage_3.document, '{ "_id" : { "$numberInt" : "1" } }'::bson, '{ "now" : NOW_SYS_VARIABLE }'::bson), '{ "_id" : { "$numberInt" : "1" } }'::bson)) NULLS FIRST
   ->  Subquery Scan on agg_stage_3
